    "summary": "This section provides quantitative time-series data on market financial performance from 2021 to 2025. It is optimized to answer retrieval queries regarding:\n- **Topics:** Market revenue scale and annual growth rate trends.\n- **Entities:** Unspecified market/industry; currency: RMB.\n- **Dates:** 2021, 2022, 2023, 2024, 2025.\n- **Definitions/Procedures:** None provided.\n- **Claims:** The market experienced fluctuating revenue with alternating periods of decline and recovery over the five-year window.\n- **Tables/Figures:** None referenced in the text.\n- **Metrics:** Annual revenue in billion RMB (2021: 174.0; 2022: 164.86; 2023: 170.22; 2024: 163.45; 2025: 165.84) and year-over-year growth rates (2021: +3.25%; 2022: -5.25%; 2023: +3.25%; 2024: -3.97%; 2025: +1.46%).\n- **Evidence Types:** Quantitative historical financial data and percentage-based performance indicators.\n- **Answerable Questions:** What were the exact market revenue figures and growth rates for each year between 2021 and 2025? Which years showed positive vs. negative growth? What was the overall revenue trajectory during this period?"
