    "summary": "This section provides chart legends and descriptive metadata for visualizations of the US mobile game market, supporting retrieval for the following:\n- **Topics & Metrics:** US mobile game market revenue scale (unit: 100M RMB), growth rate (%), and revenue concentration/share by ranking tier.\n- **Dates:** 2023, 2024, and 2025.\n- **Definitions/Legend:** Blue bars = revenue scale; cyan line = growth rate. Concentration chart color coding: blue (Top 1–10 rank), cyan (11–50), green (51–200), orange (others).\n- **Figures & Evidence Types:** Dual-axis chart (bar + line) for market scale/growth; comparative bar chart for revenue concentration across ranking tiers. Evidence is proprietary research and charting by Diandian Data (点点数据).\n- **Entities:** US mobile game market, Diandian Data (点点数据).\n- **Answerable Questions:** What do the blue bars and cyan lines represent in the market revenue chart? How is US mobile game revenue distributed across different ranking tiers from 2023 to 2025? What are the specific ranking brackets used in the concentration analysis? What is the source of the market data and visualizations? (No procedures or explicit claims are present in this section.)"
